data.description: Now available with a Social Membership to the Members Club at Marco - golf year round, and enjoy the Marco Marriott private beach club, tennis, spa, pools and discount on dining! Welcome to the upscale Rialto in Hammock Bay, minutes from Marco's dining and entertainment, and convenient to Olde Naples and the Naples beaches. This 2455 sq. ft. Turnkey condo lives like a single family home, where a private elevator awaits as you exit your 2 car garage to bring you into the second floor home. A split bedroom floor plan offers privacy for owners and guests. Huge open great room living area with high ceilings and multiple sliders overlooks the golf course offering formal dining and several gathering areas. An expansive lanai lends itself to enjoying dining and relaxing with peaceful views, spectacular sunsets and privacy. A large den/office provides workspace/additional room for guests. The lanai is protected by electric shutters, and the entire unit has impact windows and sliders. The recent tile-look metal roof will last for decades. With immaculately maintained buildings and grounds, classy paver driveways and sidewalks, you will be proud to be the new owner of this well kept home.
